opendial.inference.approximate

Class Sample

  • java.lang.Object
    • opendial.datastructs.Assignment
      • opendial.inference.approximate.Sample
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Sample>

    public class Sample
extends Assignment
implements java.lang.Comparable<Sample>
    Representation of a (possibly weighted) sample, which consists of an assignment of values together with a weight (here in logarithmic form) and utility.
    Author:
    Pierre Lison (plison@ifi.uio.no)
